---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy - TrendBriefly"
    description="TrendBriefly's Privacy Policy. How we collect, use, and protect information about visitors to getnestdaily.xyz."
    canonical="https://getnestdaily.xyz/pages/privacy-policy/"
>
    <section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>Effective date: May 2, 2026 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Last updated: May 2, 2026</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="policy-layout">
                <div class="post-content">

                    <div class="policy-intro-box">
                        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how TrendBriefly (<strong>getnestdaily.xyz</strong>) collects and uses information when you visit our website. We do not sell personal data. We do not build personal profiles for marketing. This policy is written in plain language so you know exactly what happens.</p>
                    </div>

                    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

                    <h3>Information you provide directly</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Email address</strong> - when you subscribe to our newsletter via the subscription form on the site.</li>
                        <li><strong>Email and message content</strong> - when you contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@getnestdaily.xyz">hello@getnestdaily.xyz</a>.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>We do not require you to create an account or log in to read our content.</p>

                    <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> - pages visited, time on page, referral source, and browser type, collected through Google Analytics with IP anonymization enabled.</li>
                        <li><strong>Advertising data</strong> - Google AdSense may collect data to serve relevant ads. See the <a href="#advertising" >Advertising</a> section below.</li>
                        <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> - stored in your browser's <code>localStorage</code> (not a cookie; not sent to our servers).</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>2. Cookies</h2>
                    <p>The following cookies may be set when you visit TrendBriefly:</p>

                    <div class="policy-table-wrap">
                        <table class="policy-table">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Cookie / Storage</th>
                                    <th>Set by</th>
                                    <th>Purpose</th>
                                    <th>Duration</th>
                                    <th>Type</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><code>_ga</code>, <code>_ga_*</code></td>
                                    <td>Google Analytics</td>
                                    <td>Distinguishes unique visitors for anonymous traffic reporting</td>
                                    <td>2 years</td>
                                    <td>Analytics</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><code>_gid</code></td>
                                    <td>Google Analytics</td>
                                    <td>Distinguishes users within a session</td>
                                    <td>24 hours</td>
                                    <td>Analytics</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>AdSense cookies</td>
                                    <td>Google AdSense</td>
                                    <td>Serves relevant advertisements based on browsing activity</td>
                                    <td>Varies</td>
                                    <td>Advertising</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><code>TrendBriefly-theme</code></td>
                                    <td>This site (localStorage)</td>
                                    <td>Remembers your light/dark mode preference</td>
                                    <td>Until cleared</td>
                                    <td>Functional (local only)</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <p>You can disable or delete cookies through your browser settings. Disabling analytics and advertising cookies will not affect your ability to read content on this site.</p>

                    <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>To respond to messages and inquiries sent to us by email.</li>
                        <li>To send newsletter updates to subscribers (only if you opted in; unsubscribe at any time).</li>
                        <li>To understand how readers use the site so we can improve content and navigation.</li>
                        <li>To serve advertisements through Google AdSense.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 id="advertising">4. Advertising</h2>
                    <p>TrendBriefly uses Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google AdSense may use cookies and similar technologies to show ads based on your prior browsing behaviour across the web. This is known as interest-based advertising.</p>
                    <p>You can opt out of interest-based advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a> or by using the <a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Your Online Choices</a> tool.</p>
                    <p>Google's privacy practices are described in the <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

                    <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
                    <div class="policy-table-wrap">
                        <table class="policy-table">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Service</th>
                                    <th>Purpose</th>
                                    <th>Privacy Policy</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Google Analytics</td>
                                    <td>Anonymous traffic analysis</td>
                                    <td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View</a></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Google AdSense</td>
                                    <td>Advertisement delivery</td>
                                    <td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View</a></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Website hosting &amp; CDN</td>
                                    <td>Serving web pages and static assets globally</td>
                                    <td>Provided by our hosting partner</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Google Fonts</td>
                                    <td>Typography (loaded from Google servers)</td>
                                    <td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View</a></td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>Depending on where you are located, you may have the following rights regarding any personal data we hold:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Access</strong> - request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
                        <li><strong>Correction</strong> - ask us to correct inaccurate data.</li>
                        <li><strong>Deletion</strong> - request that we delete your data.</li>
                        <li><strong>Opt-out of newsletter</strong> - unsubscribe at any time via the link in any newsletter email.</li>
                        <li><strong>Cookie opt-out</strong> - manage cookies through your browser settings or the tools listed in Section 4.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@getnestdaily.xyz">hello@getnestdaily.xyz</a> with the subject line "Privacy Request".</p>

                    <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
                    <p>Email correspondence is retained for as long as reasonably necessary to respond to your inquiry. Newsletter subscriber email addresses are retained until you unsubscribe. Analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics' default retention settings (14 months).</p>

                    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <p>TrendBriefly is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has submitted personal information to us, please contact us and we will delete it.</p>

                    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy when our practices change or when required by law. The effective date at the top of this page will be updated accordingly. Continued use of the site after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

                    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
                    <p>Questions about this Privacy Policy: <a href="mailto:hello@getnestdaily.xyz">hello@getnestdaily.xyz</a><br>
                    Or write to us via our <a href="/pages/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>

